## Content Mix Guidelines

### Monthly Content Distribution
- **40% Lifestyle/Aspirational:** Property beauty, experiences, local culture
- **30% Behind-the-scenes:** Staff stories, local partnerships, preparation
- **20% Promotional:** Packages, offers, direct booking benefits
- **10% Events/Community:** Property events, local celebrations, guest features

